for committing adultery.

11:47.582 --> 11:48.624
No, they can't.

11:48.708 --> 11:51.043
Actual laws are the only laws
that are enforceable,

11:51.127 --> 11:53.921
including the one that says
you can't create religious laws.

11:54.005 --> 11:56.507
