14:03.343 --> 14:04.885
"2 Hudson Street, 27."

14:04.969 --> 14:07.513
- Is 2 Hudson 27...
- It's my address and apartment number.

14:07.597 --> 14:10.474
Alice Cynkar, an English professor at OSU.

14:10.558 --> 14:11.683
