of the top three calamities

28:18.238 --> 28:19.697
- that just occurred.
- Charlie...

28:19.782 --> 28:22.950
I, along with most people
who don't live in Japan,

28:23.035 --> 28:25.870
am not fluent in Japanese, so I have to ask.

28:26.038 --> 28:30.291
