I don't know.

31:45.320 --> 31:48.114
I don't know,
like a little sister to me or something.

31:49.658 --> 31:51.075
Your father was an abusive alcoholic?

31:51.952 --> 31:52.952
What?

31:53.036 --> 31:56.080
