You got that in the 40 minutes

32:03.505 --> 32:05.506
that I've been sitting
here that seem like a week and a half?

32:05.591 --> 32:07.008
It's in the notes my dad left.

32:07.092 --> 32:08.884
Can I have a prescription now?

32:08.969 --> 32:10.428
- He hit you?
- Come on.

32:10.512 --> 32:11.512
He hit you, right?

32:12.180 --> 32:13.848
How many times did you
see Good Will Hunting?

32:14.141 --> 32:15.975
- He hit you?
- Yes.

32:16.059 --> 32:18.311
- He hit your mother?
- Yes.

32:18.395 --> 32:21.439
You have a brother and two sisters.
He hit them, right?

32:21.523 --> 32:24.275
Look, he didn't hit anybody
once I was old enough to hit him back.

32:24.359 --> 32:26.193
And when was that?

32:26.695 --> 32:31.073
Will, how old were you
when you had to protect

32:31.158 --> 32:33.784
your mother, your brother,

32:34.453 --> 32:36.329
and your two little sisters

32:36.788 --> 32:39.749
from a grown man
who was drunk and violent?

32:44.671 --> 32:46.839
Fifth grade.

32:46.923 --> 32:49.592
I cracked a bottle of Dewar's across his face.

32:52.763 --> 32:55.056
It's in your notes.
Why are you pursuing this line of...

32:55.140 --> 32:57.058
